Emotional Intelligence, Daily. Start now: https://www.theschooloflife.com/subscription/ 
The phone has created a new agony in modern love. This film unpacks the "Texting Wars," exploring how constant contact exacerbates the tension between anxious and avoidant attachment styles. Learn why read receipts and delayed replies become existential crises, and how to develop a calm communication strategy to manage insecurity and maintain emotional safety. #Relationships #DatingAdvice #AttachmentTheory #Texting #MentalHealth Unlock all the content of The School of Life with a subscription to our podcast, articles, videos, and exercises, specially tailored to your needs.
